  <brief_title>Optimal Oral Hypoglycaemic Agents (OHA) for Combination With Insulin Glargine (Sulfonylurea vs. Metformin)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Insulin Glargine Combined With Sulfonylurea Versus Metformin in Patients With Type 2 Diabetes: A Randomized, Controlled Trial.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
