  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Primary objective:

      To find out an optimal regimen of OHA (oral hypoglycaemic agents) in combination with insulin
      glargine (metformin, glimepiride or metformin+glimepiride) by measuring HbA1c level

      Secondary objective:

      To compare the incidence of hypoglycemia in each treatment group
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
